Symbol.Script_3D:
! Hose Cabinet
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat IF useSysMat THEN glassMaterial = sMat IF useSysMat THEN hoseMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
unID = 1
! --- FIRE HOUSE CABINET --- !
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ! Detailed
IF hoseType = 1 THEN
ADDy B/2 + ConPosY_1
tck = 0.005 doorTck = 0.01 cabinD = B ROTx 90 GOSUB 100 GOSUB 300
dfw = 0.06 ! Door Frame Width dov = 0 ! Door Overhang
ADDz B GOSUB 200 DEL 2
DEL 1 ENDIF
IF hoseType = 2 THEN
ADDy B/2 + ConPosY_1
tck = 0.005 doorTck = 0.01 cabinD = B ROTx 90 GOSUB 100 GOSUB 400
dfw = 0.06 ! Door Frame Width dov = 0 ! Door Overhang
ADDz B GOSUB 200 DEL 2
DEL 1 ENDIF ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN ! Simple
IF hoseType = 1 THEN ADDy B
tck = 0.005 doorTck = 0.01 cabinD = B ROTx 90 GOSUB 110 GOSUB 310
dfw = 0.06 ! Door Frame Width dov = 0 ! Door Overhang
ADDz B GOSUB 210 DEL 2
DEL 1 ENDIF
IF hoseType = 2 THEN
ADDy B/2 + ConPosY_1
tck = 0.005 doorTck = 0.01 cabinD = B ROTx 90 GOSUB 110 GOSUB 410
dfw = 0.06 ! Door Frame Width dov = 0 ! Door Overhang
ADDz B GOSUB 210 DEL 2
DEL 1 ENDIF ENDIF DEL TOP RESOL res
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1 = ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 14 END
100: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PRISM_ 10, cabinD, -A/2, 0, 15, -A/2, ZZYZX, 15, A/2, ZZYZX, 15, A/2, 0, 15, -A/2, 0, -1, -A/2+tck, tck, 15, -A/2+tck, ZZYZX-tck, 15, A/2-tck, ZZYZX-tck, 15, A/2-tck, tck, 15, -A/2+tck, tck, -1
PRISM_ 4, tck, -A/2+tck, tck, 15, -A/2+tck, ZZYZX-tck, 15, A/2-tck, ZZYZX-tck, 15, A/2-tck, tck, 15
HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, ZZYZX, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, ZZYZX, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, ZZYZX, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, ZZYZX, B, unID: unID=unID+1 RETURN
110: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial EXTRUDE 4,0,0,B, 1+4+16+32, -A/2, 0, 0, -A/2, ZZYZX, 0, A/2, ZZYZX, 0, A/2, 0, 0
HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, ZZYZX, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, ZZYZX, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, ZZYZX, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, ZZYZX, B, unID: unID=unID+1 RETURN
200: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PRISM_ 10, doorTck, -A/2-dov, -dov, 15, -A/2-dov, ZZYZX+dov, 15, A/2+dov, ZZYZX+dov, 15, A/2+dov, -dov, 15, -A/2-dov, -dov, -1, -A/2-dov+dfw, -dov+dfw, 15, -A/2-dov+dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 15, A/2+dov-dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 15, A/2+dov-dfw, -dov+dfw, 15, -A/2-dov+dfw, -dov+dfw, -1
MATERIAL glassMaterial POLY_ 4, -A/2-dov+dfw, -dov+dfw, 1, -A/2-dov+dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 1, A/2+dov-dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 1, A/2+dov-dfw, -dov+dfw, 1 RETURN
210: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial ADDz doorTck POLY_ 10, -A/2-dov, -dov, 1, -A/2-dov, ZZYZX+dov, 1, A/2+dov, ZZYZX+dov, 1, A/2+dov, -dov, 1, -A/2-dov, -dov, -1, -A/2-dov+dfw, -dov+dfw, 1, -A/2-dov+dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 1, A/2+dov-dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 1, A/2+dov-dfw, -dov+dfw, 1, -A/2-dov+dfw, -dov+dfw, -1
MATERIAL glassMaterial POLY_ 4, -A/2-dov+dfw, -dov+dfw, 1, -A/2-dov+dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 1, A/2+dov-dfw, ZZYZX+dov-dfw, 1, A/2+dov-dfw, -dov+dfw, 1 DEL 1 RETURN
300: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial RESOL 8
ADD -A/2+tck+1.5*ConWidth_1,ConPosZ_1,B/2 ROTz -90 ROTx 90 ARMC 1.2*ConWidth_1/2, ConWidth_1/2, 1.5*ConWidth_1, 0,0,90 DEL 1
ADDy 0.05 ROTx 90 CYLIND 1.5*ConWidth_1+0.05, 1.2*ConWidth_1/2 ADDz -0.02
RESOL 6 CYLIND 0.02, 0.2*ConWidth_1 ADDz -0.01
RESOL 8 CYLIND 0.01, ConWidth_1 DEL 6
tx = 0.03 tnum = MAX(1, INT((A-2*ConWidth_1) / (2 * tx)))
dx = tnum*tx*2-tx dy = 0.7*ConWidth_1
ADD -A/2+tck+1.5*ConWidth_1,ConPosZ_1-1.5*ConWidth_1,B/2 ROTx 90 PRISM 4, 0.01, -ConWidth_1/2, -dy, -ConWidth_1/2, dy, dx, dy, dx,-dy ADDx dx MULz -1 RESOL 8 MATERIAL hoseMaterial CONE 2*ConWidth_1, ConWidth_1/2, 0.3*ConWidth_1, 90, 90 DEL 3
px=0 ADD 0, -0.01, -0.05 FOR i=1 TO tnum PUT px, 0, 0, px, -ConPosZ_1+tx+3*ConWidth_1, 1, px+tx, -ConPosZ_1+tx+3*ConWidth_1, 1001, px+tx, 0, 0 px=px+2*tx NEXT i
RESOL 4 EXTRUDE NSP/3, 0,0, 0.1, 16+32, GET(NSP)
DEL 2 RETURN
310: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial RESOL 6
ADD -A/2+tck+1.5*ConWidth_1,ConPosZ_1,B/2 ROTz -90 ROTx 90 ARMC 1.2*ConWidth_1/2, ConWidth_1/2, 1.5*ConWidth_1, 0,0,90 DEL 1
ADDy 0.05 ROTx 90 CYLIND 1.5*ConWidth_1+0.05, 1.2*ConWidth_1/2 ADDz -0.02
ADDz -0.01 RESOL 8 CYLIND 0.01, ConWidth_1 DEL 6
tx = 0.03 tnum = INT((A-2*ConWidth_1) / (2 * tx))
dx = tnum*tx*2-tx dy = 0.7*ConWidth_1
ADD -A/2+tck+1.5*ConWidth_1,ConPosZ_1-1.5*ConWidth_1,B/2 ROTx 90 MATERIAL hoseMaterial PRISM 4, ConPosZ_1-3*ConWidth_1, 0, -dy, 0, dy, dx, dy, dx,-dy ADDx dx MULz -1 RESOL 8 CONE 2*ConWidth_1, ConWidth_1/2, 0.3*ConWidth_1, 90, 90 DEL 4 RETURN
400: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial ADD -A/2+tck+1.5*ConWidth_1,ConPosZ_1,B/2 ROTy 180 ARMC 1.2*ConWidth_1/2, ConWidth_1/2, 1.5*ConWidth_1, 0,0,90 DEL 1 ARMC 1.2*ConWidth_1/2, ConWidth_1/2, 1.5*ConWidth_1, 0,0,90
ROTx 90 ADDy 0.05 ROTx 90 CYLIND 1.5*ConWidth_1+0.05, 1.2*ConWidth_1/2 ADDz -0.02
RESOL 6 CYLIND 0.02, 0.2*ConWidth_1 ADDz -0.01
RESOL 8 CYLIND 0.01, ConWidth_1 DEL 6
ADD 0, ZZYZX/2, B/2-0.05
RESOL res CYLIND 0.12, 0.05*A
MATERIAL hoseMaterial PRISM_ 3,0.1, 0,0,979, 0.8*MIN(ZZYZX,A)/2, 360,4079, 0.05*A, 360,4079 PRISM 4,0.1, 0,-0.8*MIN(ZZYZX,A)/2, -A/2+tck+3*ConWidth_1,-ZZYZX/2+ConPosZ_1, -A/2+tck+3*ConWidth_1,-ZZYZX/2+ConPosZ_1+0.001, 0,-0.8*MIN(ZZYZX,A)/2+0.001
DEL 1 RETURN
410: MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial ADD -A/2+tck+1.5*ConWidth_1,ConPosZ_1,B/2 ROTy 180 ARMC 1.2*ConWidth_1/2, ConWidth_1/2, 1.5*ConWidth_1, 0,0,90 DEL 1 ARMC 1.2*ConWidth_1/2, ConWidth_1/2, 1.5*ConWidth_1, 0,0,90
ROTx 90 ADDy 0.05 ROTx 90 CYLIND 1.5*ConWidth_1+0.05, 1.2*ConWidth_1/2 ADDz -0.03 RESOL 6 CYLIND 0.01, ConWidth_1 DEL 5
MATERIAL hoseMaterial RESOL 12 ADD 0, ZZYZX/2, B/2-0.05 CYLIND 0.1, 0.8*MIN(ZZYZX,A)/2
PRISM 4,0.1, 0,-0.8*MIN(ZZYZX,A)/2, -A/2+tck+3*ConWidth_1,-ZZYZX/2+ConPosZ_1, -A/2+tck+3*ConWidth_1,-ZZYZX/2+ConPosZ_1+0.001, 0,-0.8*MIN(ZZYZX,A)/2+0.001
DEL 1 RETURN
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Hose Cabinet
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 AND GLOB_CONTEXT <> 22 THEN ! Top
! --- FIRE HOUSE CABINET --- !
ADD2 -A/2, B/2 + ConPosY_1
HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, -B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,0, unID: unID=unID+1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0, 1, 0, -B, 1, A, -B, 1, A, 0, 1 DEL 1 ENDIF DEL TOP
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 (SYMB_MIRRORED - NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED)) * (DrawingNum > 1) * SYMB_ROTANGLE
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * SYMB_MIRRORED, 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Hose Cabinet
EPS = 0.0001
DIM type_dim[2] type_dim[1]=`Шланг на Стойке` type_dim[2]=`Шланг в Катушке`
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "hoseTypeStr" THEN IF hoseTypeStr = type_dim[1] THEN hoseType = 1 IF hoseTypeStr = type_dim[2] THEN hoseType = 2 PARAMETERS hoseType = hoseType ENDIF
IF hoseTypeStr <> type_dim[hoseType] THEN hoseTypeStr = type_dim[hoseType] PARAMETERS hoseTypeStr = hoseTypeStr ENDIF
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z

call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
